<node id="Plantynet">
  <data key="d0">Plantynet</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Plantynet is an IT company based in South Korea. It is identified as the customer and the entity to whom the receipt was issued for the ChatGPT Plus Subscription service, which it purchased and paid for from OpenAI, LLC.

The company's physical address is 6th Floor, Uspace A-dong, 670 Daewangpangyo-ro, Bundang-gu, Sampyeong-dong, Seongnam-si, Gyeonggi-do, 13494, South Korea. Its email address is atldev@plantynet.com.

Beyond its subscription activities, Plantynet operates a Technology Research Institute. As part of its organizational functions, it is responsible for establishing development plans for this research institute, including a specific plan for the years 2026-2028.&lt;SEP&gt;A company located in Seongnam-si, Gyeonggi-do, South Korea, which purchased and paid for the ChatGPT Plus Subscription service.&lt;SEP&gt;A company that operates a technology research institute and establishes and executes various development plans.</data>
