<node id="3.4% Decline">
  <data key="d0">3.4% Decline</data>
  <data key="d1">metric</data>
  <data key="d2">The "3.4% Decline" refers to a specific and notable event characterized by a 3.4% decrease in the value of the Global Tech Index. This decline was consistently observed during midday trading, indicating a significant fluctuation within a single trading session.&lt;SEP&gt;A 3.4% decline was observed in the global tech index during midday trading.&lt;SEP&gt;A 3.4% decline was experienced by the Global Tech Index in midday trading.</data>
