<node id="Tech Giants">
  <data key="d0">Tech Giants</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Tech Giants refers to a category of large, major, and influential technology companies. These prominent technology firms are collectively characterized by having experienced significant declines in their stock value and across stock markets. The term specifically describes these entities that have seen their stock performance diminish considerably, including significant downturns in their stock performance and overall market value. Despite these recent stock market downturns and significant stock declines, these companies maintain their status as major players within the technology sector.</data>
