<node id="Investor Concerns">
  <data key="d0">Investor Concerns</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Investor Concerns refer to the worries and anxieties held by investors regarding specific market and economic factors. These concerns are primarily centered on issues such as rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty.

These investor concerns are widely attributed as significant causes or contributing factors to market selloffs and downturns, indicating their substantial impact on market performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty are attributed to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty contributed to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty are attributed as causes for the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d0d2c2192a45faa2dc81178173898e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-096f30b71c633363da29aedb33921bbe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc</data>
