<node id="Rising Interest Rates">
  <data key="d0">Rising Interest Rates</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rising Interest Rates represent a significant economic factor that consistently contributes to investor concerns and apprehension. This economic phenomenon is widely identified as a key driver behind negative market movements, directly impacting investor sentiment and leading to a subsequent reduction in overall market confidence.

Specifically, rising interest rates are a primary factor contributing to market selloffs, broader market downturns, and increased market volatility. The increase in interest rates heightens investor apprehension, making it a key concern for those in the market.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d0d2c2192a45faa2dc81178173898e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc</data>
