<node id="2.1% Gain">
  <data key="d0">2.1% Gain</data>
  <data key="d1">metric</data>
  <data key="d2">The "2.1% Gain" refers to a specific and modest increase in the stock value of Omega Energy. This gain represented a 2.1% rise in the company's stock.

Omega Energy posted this 2.1% gain, which was consistently described as modest and was notably driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy posted a modest 2.1% gain in stock value.&lt;SEP&gt;A 2.1% gain is the modest increase in stock value posted by Omega Energy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56282f4606fc56d4130b6951eb4c498d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d0d2c2192a45faa2dc81178173898e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
