<node id="Rising Oil Prices">
  <data key="d0">Rising Oil Prices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rising oil prices represent an economic factor with notable impacts on financial markets and specific companies. This phenomenon was identified as a key driver behind the stock gain experienced by Omega Energy, with some instances describing this as a modest gain. Furthermore, rising oil prices also contributed to and supported the broader rally observed in crude oil markets.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising oil prices drove Omega Energy's stock gain.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc</data>
