<node id="1.5% Rise">
  <data key="d0">1.5% Rise</data>
  <data key="d1">metric</data>
  <data key="d2">The entity "1.5% Rise" consistently refers to a specific upward movement in the value of gold futures. This term denotes a situation where the prices of gold futures have experienced an increase of precisely 1.5%. It serves as a direct measurement, indicating the exact percentage by which gold futures prices have risen.

This particular percentage increase in gold futures is sometimes observed in market conditions where investors are actively seeking safe-haven assets. Such investor behavior can contribute to the upward trajectory of gold futures prices, leading to the observed 1.5% rise.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures rose by 1.5%.&lt;SEP&gt;A 1.5% rise is the increase observed in Gold Futures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d0d2c2192a45faa2dc81178173898e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
