<node id="$2,080 Per Ounce">
  <data key="d0">$2,080 Per Ounce</data>
  <data key="d1">metric</data>
  <data key="d2">$2,080 Per Ounce represents a significant price point achieved by gold futures. This figure indicates that the price of gold futures reached this specific value. It is also noted that the price of gold futures rose to $2,080 per ounce, signifying an increase to this level. This value consistently refers to the price attained by gold futures.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by Gold futures after a 1.5% rise.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by Gold Futures.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached a price of $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by Gold Futures, indicating its value as a safe-haven asset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2</data>
