<node id="Investors">
  <data key="d0">Investors</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Investors are individuals or entities who actively participate in financial markets, engaging in the buying and selling of financial assets and the allocation or commitment of capital. Their primary objective in these activities is the expectation of a future financial return. As market participants, their decisions and actions are significantly influenced by various market conditions, external factors, and policy announcements.

A prominent characteristic of investors is their concern over prevailing market conditions, including specific anxieties such as rising interest rates, regulatory uncertainty, and broader economic factors. These concerns can profoundly impact market dynamics, sometimes leading to significant events like market selloffs. In response to such uncertainties or during market downturns, investors frequently seek safe-haven assets, such as gold futures, to protect their capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Investors are individuals or entities who allocate capital with the expectation of a future financial return.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0649ab1d8c10a2920ddb7d5471979705&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bfb82ef2f9104c844470a7787413791&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-189c87d63b8e6e2a4b59cfb0545528f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
