<node id="$87.60 Per Barrel">
  <data key="d0">$87.60 Per Barrel</data>
  <data key="d1">metric</data>
  <data key="d2">The entity "$87.60 Per Barrel" refers to a specific price point attained by crude oil in the market. This figure indicates that the price of crude oil climbed to a value of $87.60 per barrel.

Multiple reports consistently confirm that crude oil prices reached this particular level, signifying a notable increase or a new benchmark in its valuation. This price represents a point that crude oil either climbed to or was observed to have reached.&lt;SEP&gt;Crude oil prices climbed to $87.60 per barrel.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by crude oil after its rally.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by Crude Oil.&lt;SEP&gt;Crude oil prices climbed to $87.60 per barrel.&lt;SEP&gt;The price reached by crude oil, supported by supply constraints and strong demand.&lt;SEP&gt;The price of crude oil climbed to $87.60 per barrel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21</data>
