<node id="Interest Rates">
  <data key="d0">Interest Rates</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Interest rates represent the cost of borrowing money and are recognized as a key economic factor and a fundamental financial concept. They play a significant role in financial markets and contribute to overall economic stability.

A notable aspect of interest rates is the impact of their upward movement. Rising interest rates are consistently identified as a significant concern for investors, frequently contributing to heightened investor anxieties. This increase in rates is also widely attributed as a factor leading to market selloffs and influencing broader market movements.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest rates are the cost of borrowing money, identified as a concern for investors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0649ab1d8c10a2920ddb7d5471979705&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2447fe875b384c188ba9d3554399dc6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b02689c99575169a9478479eec80788c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56282f4606fc56d4130b6951eb4c498d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bfb82ef2f9104c844470a7787413791&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a55c2cba84b3e6fcdc01243ddae25b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-096f30b71c633363da29aedb33921bbe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ba233fdd570e49e5ca9f9ac3aab2be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f37adcf76bfa0b63b612de2654ab7ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc975fc447484d2d11d8799d6ecf1373&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-189c87d63b8e6e2a4b59cfb0545528f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-013979dddee9fc5949155b21705bc9be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
