<node id="LGU+">
  <data key="d0">LGU+</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">LGU+ is a telecommunications company based in South Korea. It operates as a communication carrier and is frequently mentioned in the context of customer business support initiatives.

LGU+ functions as a customer business partner of Plantynet (플랜티넷). In this collaborative capacity, LGU+ is involved with several services, including Exio (also referred to as Iksio), Child Phone Keeper (also known as Child Phone Guardian), and Youth Rate Plans (or Youth Plan).

Additionally, LGU+ has been identified as one of the communication carrier customers slated for support within the 2026 Customer Business Support project, underscoring its role as a key recipient of customer business assistance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697242</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="KT">
  <data key="d0">KT</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">KT is a prominent telecommunications company based in South Korea. It is recognized as a key communication carrier customer, particularly in the context of customer business support initiatives.

KT functions as a customer business partner of Plantynet (also known as 플랜티넷), collaborating on the provision of various services. These services include Ansim Box, Basic Ansim Internet, IPTV Set-top Box, and ACS. Furthermore, KT has been identified as one of the communication carrier customers targeted for support within the framework of the 2026 Customer Business Support project.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Korea Racing Authority">
  <data key="d0">Korea Racing Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An organization for which an illegal horse racing site detection and blocking Proof of Concept (POC) is being conducted.&lt;SEP&gt;A Biz business partner of Plantynet, involved with detecting and blocking illegal horse racing sites.&lt;SEP&gt;A Biz business partner of Plantynet, involved in detecting and blocking illegal horse racing sites.&lt;SEP&gt;A customer for whom illegal horse racing site detection blocking POC and commercialization is pursued.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5</data>
