<node id="AI Tech Lab">
  <data key="d0">AI Tech Lab</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">AI Tech Lab is an AI Technology Lab and a development lab, functioning as a department and one of the teams within the Technology Research Institute, specifically identified as Plantynet Technology Research Institute (플랜티넷 기술연구소). Its primary responsibility is the development and research of artificial intelligence technology, specializing in AI.

The lab actively contributes its personnel to various development and Technology Research Management (TRM) tasks. AI Tech Lab is also the organization associated with and responsible for the AI Prompt Project, which specifically includes Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). Additionally, its personnel are deployed to the Personalized Deep Voice Phishing Detection project (개인화 기반 딥보이스 피싱 탐지 프로젝트).

Kim Seon-jun (김선준) is affiliated with AI Tech Lab, which utilizes a diverse range of technologies, operating systems, and technology stacks in its research and development endeavors.&lt;SEP&gt;A department within 기술연구소 responsible for artificial intelligence-related technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;A lab within the Technology Research Institute, where Kim Seon-Jun is affiliated, and which utilizes various technologies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54a987a86574adfb4ad1cb14029944a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
