  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="NW Lab">
  <data key="d0">NW Lab</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">NW Lab is a research laboratory and department primarily focused on network technology development and research. It operates as an organization within the Technology Research Institute, specifically identified as the Plantynet Technology Research Institute (플랜티넷 기술연구소).

The lab specializes in network technology and is responsible for contributing its personnel to various development initiatives and TRM (Technology Research Management) tasks and projects. A notable area of its involvement includes participation in the development of personalized deep voice phishing detection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697258</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Device Tech Lab">
  <data key="d0">Device Tech Lab</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Device Tech Lab is a specialized research and development laboratory and department operating within the Plantynet Technology Research Institute (also referred to as Technology Research Institute or 플랜티넷 기술연구소). Its core mission involves the development and research of device-related technologies.

As one of the teams within the institute, Device Tech Lab contributes personnel to various development and TRM tasks, utilizing diverse technology stacks in its operations. The lab is also actively involved in projects such as the development of AI-based similar URL detection, deploying its personnel to these initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;A department within 기술연구소 responsible for device technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;A lab within the Technology Research Institute that utilizes various technologies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff117209416e691729376fe4458e772&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942fb16b5690c9bee8baf317da4683f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-415714e969887d85f795c17daca79dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
