<node id="AI">
  <data key="d0">AI</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The core technology for advancing the Ansim Platform, used for voice recognition control, Q&amp;A, and image generation.&lt;SEP&gt;An artificial intelligence system that plays the role of an AI assistant, utilizing various technologies like NLU, TTS, LLM, and Command Router to control app functions and provide services.&lt;SEP&gt;Artificial intelligence utilized for implementing various features such as the AI Assistant, AI-based voice recognition control, Q&amp;A AI, and AI creative functions.&lt;SEP&gt;A core technology intended to control Ansim Platform app functions by voice and provide various information.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific development area where technical stacks are categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;A development area and technical skill defined by the Technology Research Institute.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95087ad5658addfcfa23bfff3025dddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697539</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="NLU">
  <data key="d0">NLU</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Natural Language Understanding technology utilized by AI for voice recognition control.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural Language Understanding technology, used by the AI-based voice recognition control.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural Language Understanding, a technology used in the AI-based voice recognition control feature.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697457</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="TTS">
  <data key="d0">TTS</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Text-to-Speech technology utilized by AI for voice recognition control.&lt;SEP&gt;Text-to-Speech technology, used by the AI-based voice recognition control.&lt;SEP&gt;Text-To-Speech, a technology used in the AI-based voice recognition control feature for converting text to speech.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697457</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="LLM">
  <data key="d0">LLM</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Large Language Model utilized by AI for question-and-answer type functions.&lt;SEP&gt;LLM (Large Language Model) is used for generating answers and can suffer from outdated information and hallucination issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Model, which RAG aims to improve by addressing issues like lack of up-to-date information and hallucination.&lt;SEP&gt;A Large Language Model integrated into the question-answering AI.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Model, integrated into the Q&amp;A AI.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Model, a technology integrated into the question-answering AI feature to enable daily conversations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697457</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Command Router">
  <data key="d0">Command Router</data>
  <data key="d1">software</data>
  <data key="d2">An intermediate control hub that connects natural language commands to in-app APIs, performing automatic mapping, delivery, and result return.&lt;SEP&gt;A system utilized by AI for app function control, which extracts Intent and Entity from natural language commands, then maps and transmits them to app function APIs, acting as an intermediate control hub.&lt;SEP&gt;A middleware acting as a central control hub that analyzes natural language commands and maps them to in-app APIs for function execution.&lt;SEP&gt;A software component that maps natural language commands and connects to app function APIs.&lt;SEP&gt;An intermediate control hub that connects to in-app APIs, automatically mapping, transmitting, processing results, and returning information based on extracted natural language commands.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697457</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="앱 기능 API">
  <data key="d0">앱 기능 API</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Application programming interfaces for controlling app functions, to which Command Router maps and transmits commands.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772696660</data>
