</node>
<node id="안심 플랫폼">
  <data key="d0">안심 플랫폼</data>
  <data key="d1">product</data>
  <data key="d2">A core service platform that will be expanded and advanced using AI.&lt;SEP&gt;A platform targeting B2C and B2B2C customers, aiming to support the health, safety, convenience, and emotional well-being of seniors and family members, with a launch planned for August 2025. It includes various features and has an enhancement plan.&lt;SEP&gt;A platform whose primary users are seniors and families, aiming for the expansion and enhancement of its associated app.&lt;SEP&gt;A mobile app designed for seniors and families, which is planned to be expanded and enhanced by integrating AI features.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-077f1c8d65370143de742282e9519342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9</data>
