  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An advancement plan providing information on nursing facilities, national policies, and senior communities, with a planning period of 3 weeks.&lt;SEP&gt;A senior information provision feature included in the Ansim Platform's enhancement plan, with a planning period of 3 weeks.&lt;SEP&gt;A feature providing information for seniors, included in the Ansim Platform AI enhancement plan.&lt;SEP&gt;An enhancement plan for the Ansim Platform providing information on nursing facilities, national policies and benefits, and senior community.</data>
