  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An advancement plan including automatic medication information registration, reminders, and information provision via OCR scanning of medicine packets, with a planning period of 3 weeks.&lt;SEP&gt;A medication management feature included in the Ansim Platform's enhancement plan, with a planning period of 3 weeks.&lt;SEP&gt;A feature included in the Ansim Platform enhancement plan that uses OCR technology to scan medicine packets.&lt;SEP&gt;An enhancement plan for the Ansim Platform providing automatic medication information registration and alerts, and OCR-based medicine bag scanning.</data>
