  <data key="d0">AI 비서</data>
  <data key="d1">software</data>
  <data key="d2">An AI-powered voice control feature designed to assist senior users with app usage.&lt;SEP&gt;The role performed by AI in controlling the app, assisting senior users with voice commands.&lt;SEP&gt;An AI-powered assistant designed to control app functions and support senior users, performing roles in health/safety management, living/convenience support, and emotional/community enhancement.&lt;SEP&gt;A voice-based function utilizing AI to assist seniors in using the Ansim Platform app.</data>
