<node id="Search Quality Improvement">
  <data key="d0">Search Quality Improvement</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Search Quality Improvement is a method to enhance the relevance and accuracy of search results, part of RAG testing and advancement.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of enhancing the RAG retriever's ability to find relevant documents for a given query.&lt;SEP&gt;Enhancing the relevance and accuracy of search results in a RAG system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b</data>
