<node id="RAG System Construction">
  <data key="d0">RAG System Construction</data>
  <data key="d1">project</data>
  <data key="d2">RAG System Construction is the process of building a Retrieval-Augmented Generation system.&lt;SEP&gt;The process or project of building a RAG system.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of building a RAG system, involving several stages from Vector DB setup to testing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b</data>
