<node id="Vector DB Construction">
  <data key="d0">Vector DB Construction</data>
  <data key="d1">project</data>
  <data key="d2">Vector DB Construction is a detailed step within RAG system construction that involves designing tables, preprocessing documents, chunking, selecting embedding models, and loading embedding vectors.&lt;SEP&gt;The process or project of building a Vector DB.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific step within RAG system construction, involving document preprocessing, chunking, embedding model selection, and vector loading.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b</data>
