<node id="Prompt">
  <data key="d0">Prompt</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Prompt is an instruction or context given to an LLM to guide its response generation.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific input or instruction given to an LLM to guide its response generation.&lt;SEP&gt;Instructions or context provided to an LLM to guide its response within a RAG system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1772697212</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Answer">
  <data key="d0">Answer</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Answer is the final output generated by the LLM based on the query and retrieved documents.&lt;SEP&gt;The output response generated by the RAG system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d141f18a9aab4498557bd2c9197355e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b</data>
