  <data key="d0">AI Prompt Project (RAG)</data>
  <data key="d1">project</data>
  <data key="d2">AI Prompt Project (RAG) is a project focused on AI Prompt and Retrieval-Augmented Generation, managed by Kim Sun-jun.&lt;SEP&gt;A project focused on AI prompts and Retrieval-Augmented Generation, managed by Kim Sun-Jun.</data>
