  <data key="d8">The relation (3.4% Decline, Global Tech Index) describes a specific event concerning the performance of the Global Tech Index. This index experienced a notable decline of 3.4%.

This particular drop was observed during midday trading, indicating a significant movement within the market session. The consistent reporting across various descriptions confirms the magnitude and timing of this performance event for the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;The Global Tech Index dropped by 3.4%.</data>
