  <data key="d7">17.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between Global Tech Index and Nexon Technologies indicates a significant influence of Nexon Technologies' stock performance on the broader index. Specifically, a decline in Nexon Technologies' stock has been identified as a contributing factor to an overall drop in the Global Tech Index. This suggests that Nexon Technologies holds a notable weighting or represents a key component within the Global Tech Index, such that its individual stock movements can impact the index's aggregate performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock decline contributed to the overall drop in the Global Tech Index.</data>
