<edge source="Market Selloff" target="Tech Giants">
  <data key="d7">22.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between a Market Selloff and Tech Giants describes a scenario where Tech Giants experienced significant declines in their market value. These substantial declines among Tech Giants were a key contributing factor to the broader market selloff.

During this period of market downturn, Tech Giants were notably among the hardest-hit sectors, indicating their prominent role in both experiencing and influencing the overall market decline. The significant drops in the market value of these companies directly contributed to the wider market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants saw significant declines, contributing to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants saw significant declines, contributing to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants saw significant declines contributing to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants experienced significant declines as part of the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d9">company performance,contributed to,contributes to,decline,experience,impact,impacted by,market impact,market performance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-68766b231992936270936e6f0b183e36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0649ab1d8c10a2920ddb7d5471979705&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d0d2c2192a45faa2dc81178173898e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a55c2cba84b3e6fcdc01243ddae25b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651844ca8fc582eb9e5c5ae952cda217&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f37adcf76bfa0b63b612de2654ab7ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc975fc447484d2d11d8799d6ecf1373&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5518f677237e7383fa30dabc5ab818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a021472a4b1810bb9115f956313f4eb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbf7a61e9910d0b949699c42c00b1607&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
