<edge source="Market Selloff" target="Interest Rates">
  <data key="d7">24.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between (Interest Rates, Market Selloff) describes a causal connection where rising interest rates are identified as a significant factor leading to a market selloff. This dynamic is primarily driven by investor concerns and anxieties that arise in response to increasing interest rates.

Analysts and market observers widely attribute these investor anxieties over rising interest rates as a direct cause for periods of market selloff. The consensus indicates that the prospect of higher interest rates prompts investors to adjust their strategies, often leading to a broad decline in market values.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates are attributed as a cause for the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Analysts attribute the market selloff to investor concerns over rising interest rates.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates are attributed as a cause for the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns over rising interest rates are attributed as a cause for the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d9">attributed to,attribution,causal factor,causation,cause,caused by,economic factor,investor concern</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2447fe875b384c188ba9d3554399dc6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b02689c99575169a9478479eec80788c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56282f4606fc56d4130b6951eb4c498d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bfb82ef2f9104c844470a7787413791&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f484700b8f584c97b2a965ce95f5d752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a55c2cba84b3e6fcdc01243ddae25b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c122a1351bb62d4818744846fb8b3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ba233fdd570e49e5ca9f9ac3aab2be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a0547158026e43fb8dcad61fe81ede2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f37adcf76bfa0b63b612de2654ab7ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc975fc447484d2d11d8799d6ecf1373&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf32d76f6af2b946cb3db4a54c84bdab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2db7e0c2a92a184a27e188bc4286ed70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5c6e8c62a21c8afb975734578cc2331&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-013979dddee9fc5949155b21705bc9be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5e29f86aac7deb2036ce96b4fbd5a21</data>
