<edge source="Market Selloff" target="Federal Reserve Policy Announcement">
  <data key="d7">20.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between a Federal Reserve Policy Announcement and a Market Selloff describes a scenario where the anticipation and uncertainty surrounding the Federal Reserve's monetary policy decisions or official announcements significantly contribute to instability within financial markets.

Speculation over potential changes in Federal Reserve policy is a primary driver in this relationship. This speculation frequently leads to heightened market volatility, prompting investors to react by selling off assets. This investor selloff, driven by the uncertainty surrounding the Federal Reserve's actions, can result in a broader market decline.&lt;SEP&gt;Speculation over Federal Reserve policy changes contributed to market volatility and investor selloff.</data>
  <data key="d9">financial regulation,influences,interest rate impact,market volatility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0beb624e95d0a83ff827995041e5f87c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8de6e6c31fc329874fc387736b746d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-532256487602de4be2e3c0e854913102&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56282f4606fc56d4130b6951eb4c498d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bfb82ef2f9104c844470a7787413791&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b5730698c6919a72fa8fe9e365553a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58b3e6c838a45a3d906d10fc138ce489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-096f30b71c633363da29aedb33921bbe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4ad6777f6f372ddf6631e7703104954&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c6a355152f3149b1a67320fd1f08a52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f37adcf76bfa0b63b612de2654ab7ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9322d396cbf361d7f17eda716eeff69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-843163ef4ca10cff5a41be5865ed300f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d95555952d1fd191bad09dd2edf939dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3586dcab6b282878bcaf595ac6fd2245&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-189c87d63b8e6e2a4b59cfb0545528f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d7b67eb1f5269cf901bd85a6fa243d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b3c51912cd727db72eefcfd4ca93f3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b49052807e826628e673ce95e0a65779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873a2f7c0b11e6a65564e71b9d136ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6959a8e57f671bac210859bec155307</data>
