  <data key="d8">The relation "(7.8% Plummet, Nexon Technologies)" describes a significant financial event concerning Nexon Technologies. This event specifically indicates that Nexon Technologies experienced a substantial decline in its stock value.

The company's stock plummeted by 7.8%, signifying a notable negative movement in its market performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies saw its stock plummet by 7.8%.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies saw its stock plummet by 7.8%.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies saw its stock plummet by 7.8%.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock plummeted by 7.8%.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies' stock plummeted by 7.8%.</data>
