<edge source="Quarterly Earnings" target="Nexon Technologies">
  <data key="d7">46.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "(Nexon Technologies, Quarterly Earnings)" describes the financial performance of Nexon Technologies for a specific financial quarter. During this period, Nexon Technologies reported quarterly earnings that were lower than anticipated by market expectations.

This announcement of lower-than-expected quarterly earnings had a notable impact on the company's market standing. It subsequently led to a significant decline in Nexon Technologies' stock value, causing its stock to plummet.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies reported lower-than-expected quarterly earnings.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies reported lower-than-expected quarterly earnings.&lt;SEP&gt;Nexon Technologies reported lower-than-expected quarterly earnings.</data>
