<edge source="Commodity Markets" target="Mixed Sentiment">
  <data key="d7">23.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Commodity Markets, Mixed Sentiment) describes a state where commodity markets exhibited a mixed sentiment. This indicates that there was no clear, uniform direction in market participants' views or trading activity across various commodities. Such a condition suggests a balance of both positive and negative influences or expectations within the sector, rather than a predominant bullish or bearish trend.&lt;SEP&gt;Commodity markets reflected a mixed sentiment.&lt;SEP&gt;Commodity markets reflected a mixed sentiment.</data>
