<edge source="$2,080 Per Ounce" target="Gold Futures">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "($2,080 Per Ounce, Gold Futures)" describes a specific price point achieved by gold futures. This indicates that the market value for gold futures reached a level of $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached $2,080 per ounce.&lt;SEP&gt;Gold futures reached $2,080 per ounce.</data>
