<edge source="Investors" target="Gold Futures">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between Gold Futures and Investors describes the dynamic where investors actively seek gold futures. This behavior is primarily driven by investors' perception of gold futures as safe-haven assets, particularly during times of market uncertainty or economic instability. Consequently, this demand from investors for gold futures often leads to an increase in their market value.</data>
