<edge source="Federal Reserve" target="Rate Hikes">
  <data key="d7">40.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "(Federal Reserve, Rate Hikes)" describes a prevailing situation characterized by increasing and growing speculation concerning potential interest rate increases initiated by the Federal Reserve. This signifies a period of heightened anticipation and extensive discussion within financial markets and broader economic circles regarding the central bank's future monetary policy decisions.

The core of this relation pertains specifically to the Federal Reserve's potential adjustments to the federal funds rate. The growing speculation underscores a significant focus on the possibility of the Federal Reserve implementing rate hikes as a component of its broader economic strategy.&lt;SEP&gt;Speculation grows over potential rate hikes by the Federal Reserve.</data>
