  <data key="d7">27.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between Oil Prices and Omega Energy describes a direct causal link where rising oil prices significantly contributed to Omega Energy's financial performance. An increase in oil prices was identified as the primary driver behind Omega Energy's reported gains.

This direct correlation specifically led to an uplift in Omega Energy's stock value. The company's stock gain was consistently driven by the upward trend in oil prices, highlighting a strong positive relationship between the two entities.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's gain was driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising oil prices drove Omega Energy's stock gain.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's stock gain was driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's stock gain was driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's gain was driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's gain was driven by rising oil prices.</data>
