  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The advancement plan for the Ansim Platform includes the introduction of AI technology.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ansim Platform utilizes AI technology to expand and enhance its app functions.&lt;SEP&gt;AI is a core technology that provides various information within the Ansim Platform app.&lt;SEP&gt;AI is a core technology that controls the functions of the Ansim Platform app by voice.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ansim Platform integrates AI as a core technology for its functions.</data>
